PrecisEnactment of the ASSESSMENT OF FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS REGULATIONS, 1994 which reflect the changes made on June 1, 1992 to the laws affecting the financial services sector and in particular the procedure used for distributing the expenses incurred in administering the Trust and Loan Companies Act among the institutions subject to that Act.
